WiseGPT adds autocomplete to ChatGPT. 

Let WiseGPT suggest the next few lines for you. Tab to use the suggestion.

Additional features:
Pre-saved prompts. Create your own prompts such as "short answer" or "I am a developer".

Upcoming features:
Hotkeys for pre-saved prompts.
